          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "绕回廊穿曲径雨寒风劲，\n灯如豆人影恍位闻夜吟。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉推门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妹妹，你今日病体如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我道是谁？原来是哪里来的一个渔翁啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉笑，贾宝玉看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日气色好了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉脱蓑衣。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你头上戴笠，身上披蓑，难道你这双鞋儿，就不怕雨湿了么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这金藤笠，玉针蓑，还有一双沙棠屐，乃是一袭。是我将它脱在廊下了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此。这蓑笠倒也精巧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此乃北静王所赠。妹妹若是见喜，我便弄一套来送与妹妹。你请看这笠儿，若\n是冬天遮雪，岂不大妙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我却消受不起，要是戴上这个，不成了画上和戏上扮的渔婆子了么。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉羞。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀，这是妹妹新诗，待我看来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉看诗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "真乃绝妙好词。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉夺笺。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虽然是烧了，我已将它熟记在心里。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我要安歇了。你请回去吧，明日再来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，有打扰妹妹你劳神，我要去了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "披玉针戴金笠今宵暂别，"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢着！你有灯笼无有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "外面有一盏羊角灯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "羊角灯不亮，把这玻璃灯与你，你自己提着吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恐怕失脚滑倒将它打破！"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一个灯笼能值几何？跌了人儿，那就值得多了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "原来如此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾宝玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "风飘飘雨潇潇珍重安歇。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（贾宝玉下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "林黛玉",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "眼前人都不见芳心无赖，\n对孤灯听秋雨顾影徘徊。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（林黛玉下。）"
        }
      ],
